\section{Job status codes}{

HTCondor reports each job's status with a single letter:\tabular{ll}{
   Code \tab Meaning \cr
   I \tab Idle -- waiting for a matching execute node \cr
   R \tab Running -- currently executing \cr
   H \tab Held -- paused, usually due to an error \cr
   C \tab Completed -- finished successfully \cr
   X \tab Removed -- cancelled \cr
   S \tab Suspended \cr
}


Jobs disappear from \code{condor_q} once they complete and their output has
been transferred back to the submit node. Use \code{\link[=htc_download]{htc_download()}} to retrieve
completed job output.
}

