\section{SSH connection reuse}{

Each poll in watch mode opens a new SSH connection. Configuring
ControlMaster in your \verb{~/.ssh/config} (see \code{\link[=htc_config]{htc_config()}}) is strongly
recommended when using \code{watch = TRUE} to avoid repeated Duo MFA prompts.
